title: Split (1989).avi
description: It's an awesome sci-fi! The box/advert said there are 4-dimentional beings who know everything we say and do, and who control everything we say and do. And there is one guy who knows this, and they keep trying to capture/control him, but can't. He is going to save humanity from their influences, and bring back spontaneity.  This is for the redditor person, 2/6/14, from jinbuhuan, in nyc. Enjoy, and don't forget to seeeeed...or the bogeyman will gitchu!
